casebody.data:
Joseph R. SAHID, petitioner,
v.
CADLEROCK JOINT VENTURE, L.P. No. 12-1342. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 7, 2013.

Case below, Cadlerock Joint Venture, L.P. v. Sol Greenberg & Sons Intern., Inc., 94 A.D.3d 580 , 942 N.Y.S.2d 497 .

Motion of Philip A. Byler for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Appellate Division, Supreme Court of New York, First Judicial Department, denied.
